### This config folder is only applicable to Ubuntu platforms that use the APT package manager

In order to change the IP to static you must fill out the [netplan] file according to the following format:

network:
  version: 2
  ethernets:
    [Network Iface]:
      addresses:
        - [Your IP Address/CIDR]
      routes:
        - to: default
        - via: [Your Gateway IP]
      nameservers:
        addresses:
          - [DNS 1]
          - [DNS 2]
      dhcp4: no